@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<section id="about">
    <div class="about-1">
        <h1>ABOUT US</h1>
        <p>
            Fakhar Transport is a leading provider of transportation solutions in the state, offering reliable and
            efficient services to meet the diverse needs of its customers.
            With a fleet of modern vehicles and a dedicated team of professionals, Fakhar Transport ensures safe and
            timely journeys for passengers and cargo alike.
            Known for its commitment to quality service and customer satisfaction, Fakhar Transport plays a vital
            role in facilitating connectivity and mobility within the state's transportation network.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel" data-bs-interval="3000">
        <!-- Carousel Indicators and Items -->
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"
                    aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1"
                    aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2"
                    aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="3"
                    aria-label="Slide 4"></button>

        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="~/Images/management.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Efficient Team Management</h5>
                    <h5>
                        Our experienced team ensures seamless operations and timely departures, guaranteeing a
                        hassle-free travel experience for our passengers.
                    </h5>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/Images/seats.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Enhancing Travel Comfort</h5>
                    <h5>
                        At Fakhar Transport, we prioritize passenger comfort with well-appointed seating
                        arrangements designed for a relaxing journey.
                    </h5>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/Images/Mobile.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Building Trust Through Quality</h5>

                    <h5>
                        With a steadfast commitment to quality service, Fakhar Transport has earned the trust of our
                        customers, making us their preferred choice for reliable transportation.
                    </h5>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/Images/wifi.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Complimentary Amenities</h5>
                    <h5>
                        In addition to our exceptional service, passengers can enjoy complimentary amenities such as
                        free WiFi, enhancing their travel experience with us.
                    </h5>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
                data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
                data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>



    <div id="about-1">
        <div class="content-box-lg">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="about-item text-center">
                            <i class="fa fa-book"></i>
                            <h3>Mission</h3>
                            <hr>
                            <p>"To simplify and enhance the travel experience for individuals and families by providing a convenient, reliable, and user-friendly platform for booking bus  tickets. We are committed to ensuring safety, affordability, and accessibility for all our passengers while fostering innovation in the transportation industry."</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="about-item text-center">
                            <i class="fa fa-book"></i>
                            <h3>vision</h3>
                            <hr>
                            <p>Our vision is to become the premier choice for bus travel booking globally. We aim to    revolutionize the way people perceive and utilize bus transportation by offering seamless integration of technology, unparalleled customer service, and a wide rangeof travel options. We aspire to create a world where bus travel is not only  efficient but also enjoyable and sustainable.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>



                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="about-item text-center">
                            <i class="fa fa-book"></i>
                            <h3>HISTORY</h3>
                            <hr>
                            <p>In the early days, our platform started with a handful of bus operators and routes, serving a limited number of regions. However, through dedication, innovation, and strategic partnerships, we quickly expanded our reach and services. Over the years, we have continuously evolved, leveraging the latest technology to enhance our platform's functionality and user experience. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
